I put a patch here. It's lil dirty (no time to investigation), but solves my problem and should be start point for investigation
{code:java} 
===================================================================
--- src/main/java/http/utils/multipartrequest/MultipartRequest.java	(revision 33519)
+++ src/main/java/http/utils/multipartrequest/MultipartRequest.java	(working copy)
@@ -928,6 +928,8 @@
                     readLine(in, blockOfBytes);
 
 					String param = readParameter(in);
+                    if (strName == null)
+                        continue;
 					addParameter(strName, param);
                 }
                 else// (strFilename!=null)
{code}

